I was on my rogue in East Freeport, practicing lock pick or some such. Level 3 enchanter sends me a tell, without preamble: &quot;Do u have any stuff I can have?&quot;<br>
<br>
Me: Stuff? what kind of stuff?<br>
Him: I need stuff.<br>
Me: You're level 3, you don't need stuff, go kill some orc pawns.<br>
Him: I need stuff, I keep dying.<br>
Me: You're an ENCHANTER, get used to it.<br>
